    "multirow_a4R9He": {
      "type": "multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "row_yRKMaR": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/BlindsMeasure.jpg",
            "layout": "text_first",
            "heading": "Made-to-Measure Blinds",
            "text": "<p>Finding the perfect blinds for windows should feel exciting, not overwhelming. At Cheap Blinds, every blind is made to measure for a precise fit with no compromises. Enjoy a balance of quality materials and affordable pricing, with delivery available across Dubai and the UAE.</p><p>From sun-filled living rooms to calm bedrooms and functional bathrooms, explore a wide range of colours, fabrics, and designs that elevate every space. Roller, Roman, Vertical, Zebra; whatever your style, you will find it here.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_cWjFtP": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/qulityblinds.jpg",
            "layout": "text_first",
            "heading": "High Quality Blinds at Prices You’ll Love",
            "text": "<p>Perfectly fitted blinds don’t just improve the look, they enhance comfort too. Our easy measuring guides help you get accurate results, so your blinds sit exactly as they should.</p><p>Quality is at the core of everything we do. By working online, we reduce extra costs and pass those savings on to you, giving you premium window blinds at genuinely affordable prices.</p><p>Stylish, durable, and budget-friendly, all in one place.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_xfn4DD": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Help.jpg",
            "layout": "text_first",
            "heading": "Here to Help, Every Step of the Way",
            "text": "<p>Questions, ideas, or need a second opinion? Our friendly team is always ready to assist. From choosing the right style to placing your order, support is just a call or message away.</p><p>Customer satisfaction is a priority, and every detail is handled with care to ensure a smooth and stress-free experience from start to finish.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
