    "info_text_blocks_ifAAe8": {
      "type": "info-text-blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "info_block_NxP7Hh": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Premium Blinds for Windows Across the UAE",
            "content": "<p>At Cheap Blinds, we specialise in providing high-quality, made-to-measure window blinds at prices that genuinely surprise in the best possible way. Every blind is custom-made to your exact measurements, ensuring a perfect fit that off-the-shelf products simply cannot match, no guesswork, no compromise.</p><p>Our commitment to quality runs through every thread and mechanism we use. From blackout roller blinds that block the fierce Gulf sun and protect your family's sleep, to light-filtering zebra blinds that frame your panoramic Burj Khalifa views without sacrificing privacy, every product in our range is built to enhance your UAE home while performing beautifully in our unique climate. We don't just sell blinds; we deliver a better way to live with light.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "info_block_yjFGp8": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Blinds Made Easy — From Dubai to Fujairah, Every Step of the Way",
            "content": "<p>Shopping for window blinds online has never been easier, and we've designed the entire <a href=\"https://cheapblinds.ae/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cheapblinds.ae</span></a> experience with that in mind. Our intuitive website walks you through the full journey from browsing blind types and fabrics to entering your measurements and completing your order, all from the comfort of your sofa in Business Bay or your office in DIFC. No showroom visits, no pushy sales calls, no waiting around.</p><p>And because we know that choosing the right blind can feel daunting, especially with the wealth of fabric choices, colours, and configurations available, we offer a complimentary fabric sample service. Request up to 5samples completely free, and have them delivered to your UAE address so you can see exactly how each fabric responds to your natural light, your room's colour palette, and the unique quality of sunlight streaming through your windows. When you're ready, you can confidently buy window blinds online in just minutes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "info_block_BFDVeN": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Choosing the Right Colour for Your Home",
            "content": "<p>Colour is one of the most powerful tools in interior design, and in the UAE, where interiors range from modern minimalist Downtown lofts to richly layered Arabian-inspired villas, getting it right is everything. Our palette spans the full spectrum: timeless neutrals like warm Sand White, Desert Cream, and Pearl Grey that complement the UAE's light-filled spaces beautifully, through to bolder statement shades like Midnight Teal, Terracotta Dune, and Deep Charcoal for those who want their windows to make an impression.</p><p>Our Shop by Colour feature makes browsing effortless. Simply select your preferred hue and explore every blind style available in that shade. Better still, our free samples service means you'll never have to guess how a colour performs in your specific light conditions. The afternoon light in a Palm  Jumeirah villa facing the Gulf is a world apart from a north-facing apartment in Al Hamra Village; our samples let you see the difference before you commit.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "info_block_CqPRbk": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Fast UAE Delivery & Round-the-Clock Customer Support",
            "content": "<p>We know that once you've found your perfect blinds, waiting is the last thing you want to do. That's why Cheap Blinds offers <strong>free next-day delivery on most orders</strong> across the UAE. Whether you're moving into a new apartment in Dubai, finishing the final touches on a villa, or simply ready to refresh a room today, our fast and reliable delivery network has you covered.</p><p>Our dedicated UAE customer support team is available <strong>seven days a week</strong> to assist you at every stage, from advice on how to measure your windows correctly, to guidance on which blind type suits your room best, to post-delivery fitting support. With thousands of 5-star reviews from customers across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, and beyond, you can shop with complete confidence knowing you're in exceptionally capable hands.</p>"
          }
        },
        "info_block_3ct8Jb": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Choose Cheap Blinds?",
            "content": "<p>With years of dedicated experience serving UAE homeowners, Cheap Blinds has become the trusted name for made-to-measure window blinds across the Emirates. We combine the unbeatable convenience of 24/7 online ordering with the quality and precision of true bespoke craftsmanship, giving you the best of both worlds at prices that reflect our online-first model. No showroom overheads means every dirham of savings goes directly back to you.</p><p>Add our 2-year quality guarantee, UAE climate–tested fabrics, free samples, and smart motorised options compatible with Google Home and Alexa, and Cheap Blinds is simply the most complete, most confident blind-buying experience in the UAE. If you're planning to buy window blinds online, this is where style, value, and reliability come together.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
